ABOUT MY WORK

Fuel Nutrition

February 2019

Project Type
Design Strategy
Time Frame
1 Month

Fuel Nutrition is a sports supplement store specifically targeted for young me. The client was looking to expand his business by opening up a flagship salon operating under the same brand.

Although I was hired to put together a design concept package, this project evolved to include a set of business strategies and action items for the client to consider in order to strengthen the Fuel Nutrition brand image.
